                    <a class="btn brown lighten-1 waves-light waves-effect white-text staff-inactive-active-btn" ng-show="showDentistArchived" ng-click="toggleDentistArchiveF()"><i class="material-icons left">archive</i>Show Active</a>
                    @*Dentist Table*@
